Former Manchester United star, Michael Owen, has made his predictions for this weekend’s Premier League actions. His predictions include Manchester United’s game against Southampton and Liverpool’s meeting with Burnley. Owen is expecting a tough game for Ralf Rangnick’s side, but thinks they will secure a narrow 2-1 win. For Liverpool’s clash against Burnley at Turf Moor on Sunday, Owen expects Jurgen Klopp’s side to come out victorious this weekend. Owen’s Premier League predictions according to Metro: Man Utd 2-1 Southampton Watford 0-1 Brighton Brentford 1-2 Crystal Palace Everton 2-0 Leeds Norwich 0-3 Man City Tottenham 1-1 Wolves Newcastle 1-1 Aston Villa Burnley 0-2 Liverpool Leicester 1-2 West Ham.